        <updateDate>2004-12-01T16:42:10Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Comptroller of the Currency Accountability Act -Amends Federal law to prohibit the Comptroller of the Currency from incurring any obligation for administrative expenses in carrying out authorized activities for any fiscal year in excess of the amount provided in advance in an appropriation Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
